<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang='en'>
<head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8'>
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0'>
    <title> Welcome </title>

    <style>
        .container {
            background: #181818;
            padding: .8em;
            border-radius: .5em;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .header { 
            width: 100%;
        }

        .header.a {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .logo {
            width: 20%;
        }

        h2 {
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
        } 

        .bodyContent {
            font-size: .8rem;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .bodyContainer {
            
        }

        .footer {
            font-size: .6rem;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1em 0;
        }
        
        .linksContainer {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .divider {
            opacity: 0.2;
        }
        
        li {
            list-style: none;
            text-decoration: underline;
            margin: .4em;
            font-size: .6rem;
        }

        h4 {
            color: white;
        }

        .footerContainer {
        }
    </style>
</head>
    <body class='container'>
        <span class='header'>
            <a href='blendot.com'>
                <img src='../views/assets/logo.png' alt='Blendot official logo' class='logo' />
            </a>
        </span>
        <hr class='divider' />
        <section class='bodyContainer'>
            <h2> Welcome! </h2>

            <p class='bodyContent'>Hi {{fullNames}} {{lastName}},</p>
            <p class='bodyContent'> 
            Thank you for subscribing to our newsletters. The website is still under-development and we will let you know when we are back in business.
            All the news regarding the progress of our website, official announcements, new features and much more will be emailed to you.
            <br />
            <br />
            </p> 
        </section>
        <hr class='divider' />
        <footer class='footerContainer'> 
            <p class='footer'>
                This was emailed to {{email}} because you have subscribed to our mailing lists. 
            </p>
            <ul class='linksContainer'>
                <li> <a href='blendot.com'> Privacy Policy </a> </li>
                <li> <a href='blendot.com'> Terms of Use </a> </li>
                <li> <a href='blendot.com'> Unsubscribe </a> </li>
            </ul>
            <p class='footer'> Copyright Â© 2022 Blendot. All Rights Reserved. Logos and "Blendot" are registered trademarks of Blendot (Pty) Ltd. </p>
        </footer>
    </body>
</html>
